text.2: It's pretty cynical to cast election officials' human errors as "voter fraud." But of course it's not aimed at them; it's aimed at undermining the process in the eyes of voters. Our latest Factually newsletter from @AmPress and @Poynter w/@HarrisonMantas https://t.co/rJOBSeV8GE
